1. setup drupal ecommerce kickstart
2. install "epesi_commerce" module
3. Set "multilingual with translations" in structure on:
- content types: "basic page", 
- menus: "main menu"
- taxonomy: "Product category" - set "localize" option
4. /admin/commerce/config/currency/handling - Enable dedicated price fields for Epesi Products - for each currency you support
5. Enable "currency selector" block
6. /admin/structure/types/manage/epesi-products/fields/body - click "Enable translation" and confirm
7. set your contact us, rules pages
8 /admin/commerce/customer-profiles/types/billing/fields/commerce_customer_address - select "Name (First name, Last name)", "Organisation (single line)" and unselect "Name (single line)"
  OPTIONAL: /admin/commerce/customer-profiles/types/billing/fields - add Phone text field
9. move your banners, boxes, polls, pages etc. to drupal ads, blocks, polls, pages
10. export newsletters recordset from epesi (it will be deleted)
11. run migration.php
12. set drupal url with administrative user/password in epesi ecommerce administration panel
